Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.35,0:01:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看電影？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.35,0:01:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.25,0:01:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來打算跟朋友一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.19,0:01:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還花了錢去買指定席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.96,0:01:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果她突然不能去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說，就我們兩個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.73,0:01:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過就算補習班沒課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.57,0:01:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長還是得讀書對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.21,0:01:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.94,0:01:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這倒不是問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我真的有這個榮幸嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.51,0:01:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是兩人單獨出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.31,0:01:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.28,0:01:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.28,0:02:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳不嫌棄的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.75,0:02:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.08,0:02:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.15,0:02:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.02,0:02:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就明天11點，電影院前見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.57,0:02:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是所謂的約會嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.07,0:02:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，等等喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.58,0:02:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#10 ちぃ，相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮果然也都沒有任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.00,0:02:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都跟那個在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.91,0:03:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直沒有從\N和那個在一起的美夢中醒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟那個在一起的時光是場夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如夢般的美好時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.15,0:03:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個能實現你任何願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.32,0:03:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能按 照每個人想要的方式去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.83,0:03:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個不是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.90,0:03:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以能成為人的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.40,0:03:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.30,0:03:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個只有一件事辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個不能變成人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.64,0:03:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算能成為替代品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.38,0:03:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能變成人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.75,0:03:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事我很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.35,0:03:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我，所以很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.65,0:03:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.12,0:03:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.03,0:03:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有點事要去找新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.23,0:03:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保，新保你在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.04,0:04:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.37,0:04:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約會的秘訣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.11,0:04:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是雜誌上常寫的那種啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.11,0:04:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如約會穿的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或約會穿的內褲之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是說做什麼事會被女孩子討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.68,0:04:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以我的經驗而言，首先…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.12,0:04:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好整理你那個鳥窩頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.22,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說，外表是很重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整理頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來是約會當天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.40,0:04:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一見面先讚美她穿的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.00,0:04:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用力讚美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.03,0:04:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讚美她穿的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後你就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿出一朵玫瑰花咬在嘴裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.64,0:04:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳著探戈的舞步，來個單手倒立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳探戈的舞步倒立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.08,0:04:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的，騙你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.45,0:04:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是沒跟女孩子約會過？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.82,0:04:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說你是在室男囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.79,0:05:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也難怪會這麼慌張了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.53,0:05:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過\N我認為約會的秘訣只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.70,0:05:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.00,0:05:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡量讓自己表現得像平常一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.04,0:05:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人再怎麼想改變自己的個性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.74,0:05:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也無法像電腦一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修改程式就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.78,0:05:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能聽天由命了不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.05,0:05:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何況如果只有在約會時\N才刻意偽裝自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.85,0:05:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對約會對象也很失禮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話是沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.49,0:05:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就以脫離在室男\N為目標而努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我在室男啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表現得像平常的自己是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.56,0:05:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過頭髮還是整理一下比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.77,0:05:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差…差不多是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.61,0:05:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，沒有漏刷的部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.61,0:05:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手帕、錢包、面紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小地圖、約會指南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上肚子痛時吃的腸胃藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.22,0:06:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就準備完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.83,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有東西忘了帶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹忘了這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.96,0:06:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹忘了帶好料的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用帶好料的去，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.04,0:06:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來一整天要跟裕美一起過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.78,0:06:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還早，不過約會嚴禁遲到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.45,0:06:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你好像很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有露出那種表情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,補習班有什麼高興的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.46,0:06:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是去補習班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.53,0:06:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是要去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟打工店裡的女孩一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.64,0:06:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說去玩其實也只有兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.41,0:06:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也可以算是約會啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.81,0:06:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是兩個互相有好感的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.88,0:07:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一起快樂地玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.35,0:07:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好感？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜歡的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.69,0:07:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡那個女孩嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.47,0:07:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能說是喜歡她啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是個很好的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.08,0:07:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一個人出門嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.79,0:07:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有點事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ看家嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.29,0:07:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.59,0:07:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.53,0:07:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.71,0:08:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天也在尋找只屬於我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.01,0:08:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我，而喜歡上我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.42,0:08:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我無法實現夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.15,0:08:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也會喜歡我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.86,0:08:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有那種人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.53,0:08:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的會只喜歡我一個人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（能那樣最好了）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.37,0:08:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人真的不會對我有所要求嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（如果不是這樣…）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.45,0:08:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是因為單純喜歡我\N而跟我在一起的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.05,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他就不是只屬於我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，他在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.53,0:09:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定就在離我身邊不遠之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.44,0:09:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信一定有人會喜歡我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.61,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡等就可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我太早來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.56,0:09:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美，妳到的時間剛剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.56,0:09:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是我的手錶快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.47,0:09:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，嚇我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害妳平白忙著趕過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.37,0:09:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.04,0:09:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還好沒讓學長等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.75,0:09:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次約會就跟這麼可愛的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.79,0:09:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我此生無悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.42,0:09:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.89,0:09:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的髮型  跟平常不太一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.43,0:09:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.19,0:10:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會，感覺比較成熟，很適合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.96,0:10:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我比較喜歡學長平常的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.64,0:10:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，你怎麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用恢復原狀也沒關係啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.47,0:10:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我也比較習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以抱你的手嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.63,0:10:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.83,0:10:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不想回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.77,0:10:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是真發生這種事那該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.48,0:10:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說“妳父親會擔心”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.15,0:10:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後送她回家嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.78,0:10:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，女孩子都這麼說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.52,0:10:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候應該…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.62,0:10:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，你怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.60,0:11:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是那個人不喜歡我怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.24,0:11:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是喜歡上我以外的人怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.28,0:11:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人心不能像那個一樣\N可以任意刪除增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.01,0:11:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以很難改變人已經決定的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.99,0:11:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人心雖然善變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.79,0:11:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也有堅定不變的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.36,0:11:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是喜歡的這種情感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.36,0:11:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法輕易改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.16,0:11:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼該怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.10,0:11:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候我就得做出決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.94,0:11:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須為他做出決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.74,0:11:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我與另一個我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.44,0:12:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在呼喚著ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.26,0:12:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.27,0:12:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我傳送影像給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.21,0:13:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳一直在呼喚著我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.15,0:13:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，是我在呼喚妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.92,0:13:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼跟ちぃ有相同的臉孔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.92,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我就是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.80,0:13:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的資料都消失了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.80,0:13:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳現在跟誰在一起？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.84,0:13:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.28,0:13:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹把ちぃ撿了回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.78,0:13:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.91,0:13:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是妳的新名字嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ是ちぃ的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹取的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.45,0:13:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個秀樹是“只屬於我的人”嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.22,0:13:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.06,0:13:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只喜歡我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ醒來後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.17,0:14:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只知道秀樹教過我的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.81,0:14:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.84,0:14:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的全都忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.01,0:14:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.45,0:14:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起決定的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們又聯繫起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.83,0:14:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後妳所看到的\N做的、知道的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都會傳到我這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.01,0:14:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.88,0:14:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再見，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.67,0:15:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為要請學長吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我特別努力做了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，這是咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.81,0:15:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.78,0:15:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過能和裕美看電影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.72,0:15:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在公園吃她親手做的便當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.15,0:15:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.99,0:15:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，那就拜託妳去買東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買完就可以回家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.14,0:15:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子好餓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉麵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是拉麵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.67,0:15:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我發現一家好吃的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擔心嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.51,0:15:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫作ちぃ對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.15,0:15:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.42,0:16:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還是老樣子，什麼都不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.66,0:16:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過很可愛對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.63,0:16:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在有點不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.00,0:16:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為每台電腦都很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.47,0:16:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦也會變成\N學長最喜歡的東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.34,0:16:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方可是電腦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.41,0:16:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然真的非常可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.48,0:16:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.88,0:16:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還是跟人不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.98,0:16:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.92,0:16:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我盡是說些奇怪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.46,0:16:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去划船？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.22,0:16:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了道歉，租船費我出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦，我來出就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.13,0:16:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連午餐都讓妳請了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.26,0:16:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點錢就讓我出吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.97,0:16:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.51,0:16:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，會不會很重？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不會，輕的很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.71,0:17:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.05,0:17:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是稔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.55,0:17:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.59,0:17:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽見嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.33,0:17:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.29,0:17:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，站起來很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.14,0:17:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.01,0:17:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事，沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.81,0:17:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你看起來好像很冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.95,0:17:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.98,0:17:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去買替換的襪子和拖鞋來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.22,0:17:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了啦，裕美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.06,0:17:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帶她到附近的便利商店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.59,0:17:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也好，拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.67,0:18:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…是人類對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.88,0:18:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說裕美？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.48,0:18:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.21,0:18:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.35,0:18:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為本須和的電腦很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.05,0:18:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心你會迷上電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.89,0:18:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對人類失去興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.26,0:18:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼連稔都說同樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.66,0:18:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.89,0:18:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛裕美也說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.06,0:18:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問我電腦會不會變成\N我最喜歡的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼回答她的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.44,0:18:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說電腦還是跟人不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.27,0:18:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.21,0:18:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明早就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.08,0:18:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦跟人不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的電腦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是指柚姬嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.22,0:18:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.12,0:18:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想說的話也不用勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.46,0:18:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.83,0:18:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你對柚姬的態度不太一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常常有人說你是個好人對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.40,0:19:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.64,0:19:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你是只會被稱讚是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻交不到女朋友的類型  對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.11,0:19:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.28,0:19:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.35,0:19:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我照兩年前\N病逝的姊姊模樣做出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是外表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.26,0:19:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連個性資料\N我也盡可能的輸入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.80,0:19:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所記得的姊姊的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.30,0:19:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的東西、喜歡的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.87,0:19:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能的將\N我對姊姊的回憶全都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.21,0:19:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，柚姬很像我姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.45,0:19:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.95,0:19:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，不管有多像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.85,0:19:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都只是程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.52,0:20:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,製造柚姬的我\N是最清楚這點的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.43,0:20:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時候我會想要忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.87,0:20:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘記柚姬只是電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見面時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.34,0:20:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我別喜歡上電腦\N也是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.28,0:20:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.61,0:20:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是根據親身經驗而給你的忠告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會太多管閒事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.35,0:20:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.05,0:20:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.52,0:20:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.86,0:20:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候我不知道\N該說什麼話安慰你才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.56,0:20:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是個好人，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.00,0:20:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.17,0:20:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能早日脫離在室男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.10,0:20:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.47,0:20:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你知道這件事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.37,0:20:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為昨天新保用六倍大的字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄了一封郵件給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.08,0:20:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很高興的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真羨慕柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.56,0:21:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.74,0:21:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.11,0:21:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.48,0:21:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時候會想要忘記…是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.85,0:21:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.75,0:21:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.06,0:21:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.97,0:21:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.57,0:21:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.47,0:21:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.61,0:21:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.48,0:22:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.62,0:22:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.01,0:22:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的走在熟悉的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.01,0:22:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確會照映在眼簾中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.95,0:22:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在成群結隊前進的人群中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.13,0:22:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那顆遭到淹沒         感到膽怯的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.97,0:22:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison         d'etre         像那種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.51,0:23:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison         d'etre         如同那般的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.84,0:23:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡笑、沉沒、漂流\N究竟是為了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.78,0:23:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找著那把鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.59,0:23:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷的在尋找著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.72,0:23:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.03,0:23:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那扇門的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.08,0:23:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然摒氣傾聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.28,0:23:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎聽不見追來的腳步聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.72,0:23:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算逃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.09,0:23:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬆了口氣抬頭往上一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.26,0:23:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一顆男人的頭顱\N浮在空中對我笑著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.53,0:24:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.50,0:24:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.70,0:24:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，確認」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.84,0:24:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭顱…頭顱…
